s. The calculated magnetocrystalline anisotropy energy is large as well.\nAll 4d/Fe/W(001) films are potential candidates for complex non-collinear spin\nstructures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Aug 2021 08:31:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-22"}
