iation of the neural network weight distribution can\nbe interpreted as a renormalization flow in the space of networks. We focus on\ntranslations invariant kernels and provide preliminary numerical results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Aug 2021 10:36:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Feb 2022 18:36:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-01"}
