mperature $T$, number of ions in a given cluster $N$ and\nthe strength of super-exchange interaction $J$, obtained from both approaches\nwill be presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Aug 2021 13:01:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-04"}
