ed girder model, the flutter\nderivatives are also extracted by least square method in uniform flow to cross\nvalidate the newly-proposed approach. The identified results by two different\napproaches are compatible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Aug 2021 13:28:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-19"}
